{"tid":2446936,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【軸心國】中國俄羅斯伊朗朝鮮等國 欲以「捍衛聯合國憲章」之名 反對單方面制裁及使用武力","createTime":"2021-03-14T23:10:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T00:42:32.000Z","uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2e783b650804ec929d2459012d1534abe941c0","tid":2446936,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:10:10.000Z","msg":"路透社星期四（3月11日）看到的一份信函稱，<strong><span class=\"red\">中國、俄羅斯、朝鮮和伊朗等國成立了一個聯盟，通過反對使用武力或是武力威脅以及單方面製裁，來捍衛聯合國憲章。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n在美國總統拜登的新一屆政府加強多邊參與並改善與盟國關係之際，<strong><span class=\"red\">有16個國家和巴勒斯坦組成了&ldquo;捍衛聯合國憲章之友小組&rdquo;。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n路透社看到一份<strong><span class=\"red\">該小組的簡介（concept note）文件中提到，多邊主義&ldquo;目前正受到前所未有的攻擊，而這又會威脅到全球和平與安全&rdquo;。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>一名不願透露姓名的歐洲高級外交官回應說:&ldquo;這些所謂的朋友是違反聯合國憲章最多的人。也許他們應該從尊重自己國家的人權和基本自由開始。&rdquo;</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n小組的其他成員還包括阿爾及利亞、安哥拉、白俄羅斯、玻利維亞、柬埔寨、古巴、厄立特里亞、老撾、尼加拉瓜、聖文森特和格林納丁斯、敘利亞和委內瑞拉。<br />\n<br />\n文件還說：&ldquo;世界上越來越多國家訴諸單邊主義，其特點是孤立主義和武斷行動，包括實施單邊強制措施或是退出具有里程碑意義的協議和多邊機構，乃至試圖破壞應對共同和全球挑戰的重要努力。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n在特朗普的領導下，美國宣布退出世界衛生組織、聯合國人權理事會、聯合國文化機構教科文組織（UNESCO）、全球氣候協議和伊朗核協議。<br />\n<br />\n拜登上任後，美國決定重返世衛和巴黎氣候協議，美國還重新與總部設在日內瓦的人權理事會接觸，並尋求重新加入國際核協議。<br />\n<br />\n北京一直在聯合國努力擴大全球影響力，挑戰美國傳統領導角色，而拜登承諾在聯合國與中國較量。<br />\n<br />\n（本文依據了路透社的報導）"},{"pid":"f9abe1b4fefa559d5c68d6e2da07a9781dbe4d76","tid":2446936,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:10:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/China-Iran-North-Korea-seek-support-at-UN-to-push-back-against-unilateral-force-sanctions-20210312/5812235.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2FChina-Iran-North-Korea-seek-support-at-UN-to-push-back-against-unilateral-force-sanctions-20210312%2F5812235.html&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfMo9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=74210fcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/China-Iran-North-Korea-seek-support-at-UN-to-push-back-against-unilateral-force-sanctions-20210312/5812235.html</a>"},{"pid":"a404da0ffb121cc6ab53b044c2fddf2ab0dfebf8","tid":2446936,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:14:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nZpak-79jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnZpak-79jpg&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfMo9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=0d55eac3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nZpak-79jpg</a>"},{"pid":"756226d3caf508ca633eef1e4238a417e3e85f66","tid":2446936,"uid":61994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:21:43.000Z","msg":"又開始寫故仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef9d66b6cc80dfe1e6e575b325d07c98821b00e","tid":2446936,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023a07e7f3bfea4a41d746d4395192a3a16d5e69","tid":2446936,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:39:44.000Z","msg":"『聯合國憲章』需要共匪捍衛? 盞得啖笑"},{"pid":"b27fcc9eda8717b5ba5237fbaa3fd563ddcc4ebe","tid":2446936,"uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:56:35.000Z","msg":"清君側<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576e917ccc15a910ab4ec9fcbbb51391e161f464","tid":2446936,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:13:38.000Z","msg":"德國自己又批評美國制裁伊朗？叫佢快d解除制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449ce4dd787b24f0651611b83e7bc8ecbc34ae30","tid":2446936,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:17:46.000Z","msg":"世界毒瘤跳哂出黎"},{"pid":"f7c64c19573c7efacea832c77fabd5dbf4927248",